{"tid":1405912,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟打算轉行做社工，咁多位師兄可唔可以比d 意見我？","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T00:21:11.000Z","uid":55227,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3b07a2ef43b0de9b9da4661f89330f734de418bb","tid":1405912,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"講小小小弟背景先，<br />\n非三大bba  grad, 做咗兩年野，穩緊14k ，因為中間轉過行同埋去過working holiday, <br />\n積蓄唔多，得15k，無父幹。<br />\n<br />\n轉行原因係因為小弟出身係一個破碎家庭，所以想做d 有意義ge 野，去帶比底下階層ge 人一d 正面ge 影響，加上之前遇到一個好好ge 社工，開解jor 自己好多。<br />\n<br />\n但係我唔肯定自己係咪好適合做呢行，因為我知道做社工都好多黑暗野，如果真係想幫人，不如直接去做義工，但自己真係想試試，想入ngo 做pw 去了解多d呢個行業，岩就讀個master 入行。<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩高見？"},{"pid":"f7e7e8dd88042b5b8c91ccf0f4297b77797e9bd9","tid":1405912,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:46:33.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"4d3f9eb1d497c0b556961cbf7cd82912e5dc13b2","tid":1405912,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:49:12.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"2056dfeb1f837ac72ecef50a63e70f2188c86ad2","tid":1405912,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:53:58.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"c39cb16d9bfad18ce4b5b8656e2eb3cefbb3eb60","tid":1405912,"uid":13480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"得15k點讀master"},{"pid":"3742e29d4bebde8c8af6d0d3d50de64f2529f5ca","tid":1405912,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c39cb16d9bfad18ce4b5b8656e2eb3cefbb3eb60","tid":1405912,"uid":13480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"得15k點讀master"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:58:09.000Z","msg":"如果真係決定做，就一路做野一路草錢讀"},{"pid":"05c886b36bf2c065bd4584aa3c43d54b38c89bef","tid":1405912,"uid":58315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:59:10.000Z","msg":"要識得在制度，文書之中走位，交數之餘不忘初心。另外先要瞭解自己有無承擔別人問題、缺點的耐性。因為做野經常見到不如意的事。"}