b0c088d9ac1c398c4bc3b","tid":1405912,"uid":249699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"MSW一個廿幾萬，pt讀實習個800粒鐘都幾難頂<br />\n有經濟困難學上面師兄講可以借學資處<br />\n<br />\n社工讀個陣會好開心，但做落會係另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心頭唔高讀完肯搵點都有工（正路點都搵到份20頭嘅swa做，叻仔咪搵到ASWO或介乎SWA aswo中間嘅位），差在係咪自己想做嘅field<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同field做嘅野好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nyouth搞活動小組program多（外展就case)、院舍搞行政家屬同case野、Ifsc/iccmw/DECC個d就outreach同乜都有、CD就愈來愈少：收集下社區意見/倡議/遊行/記招/請願<br />\n<br />\n諗左field再搵識嘅社工問下工作內容了解下先"},{"pid":"25d8b573fb6f0eb265fa358a8c89f2a2a55ce13e","tid":1405912,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:13:44.000Z","msg":"不要說底下階層<br />\n試著說基層"},{"pid":"564f3b387864bb6bee65850a20d168c7dfc7d734","tid":1405912,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:23:01.000Z","msg":"社工又講heart又講原則又搵唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895981a4af1e4896cb41cd440e83f2f881df8faa","tid":1405912,"uid":113085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"你有冇了解過社工做啲咩先?<br />\n<br />\n上面有師兄講得岩呀，要識得在制度，文書之中走位。<br />\n<br />\n比如,醫務社工既責任係快啲趕人出院，唔理出邊有冇支授，都會說服你出院。<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就做NGO幫老人家搞活動。"},{"pid":"227b0f54aa29902bfa916d0fc21fe68381453f35","tid":1405912,"uid":270872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"做下義工explore 下先？"},{"pid":"d980a153f11b320b2eb490b6c2d156d92512f742","tid":1405912,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"227b0f54aa29902bfa916d0fc21fe68381453f35","tid":1405912,"uid":270872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"做下義工explore 下先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"我有穩緊義工做啊，主要係穩青少年"},{"pid":"5e4197ac0d4438c